00:21:56.880 --> 00:21:57.920
Yang?

00:22:02.400 --> 00:22:03.520
Apakah kamu masih tidak mengerti?

00:22:06.800 --> 00:22:10.040
Pengagum Jhanak.

00:22:13.720 --> 00:22:14.680
Teja?

